  <brief_title>Study of the Effect of a Fermented Dairy Product on Gastrointestinal Well Being in Adult Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;Effect of the Consumption of a Fermented Dairy Product on Gastrointestinal Well-being in a Healthy Population of Women With Minor Digestive Symptoms&quot;</official_title>
  <sponsors>
