  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of a commercially available fermented
      dairy product containing probiotics (4 weeks, twice a day) on the improvement of
      gastrointestinal well being and digestive symptoms in adult women reporting minor digestive
      troubles among the general population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
